{"tid":1035720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"O記破軍火庫拉兩男女 撿18槍3千發子彈","createTime":"2019-02-24T19:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T07:02:36.000Z","uid":40049,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"83b24d997c0ecc630e8a52a38c409b40c349011b","tid":1035720,"uid":40049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T19:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1551008843_e57a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1551008843_e57a.jpg&h=628000ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1551008843_d06d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1551008843_d06d.jpg&h=1abc0e4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1551008846_109d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1551008846_109d.jpg&h=d1c303ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科（O記）於2月21日在旺角及沙田拘捕兩名分別44及46歲的本地男女，涉嫌無牌管有槍械或彈藥。行動中，探員共撿獲14支手槍、4支長槍、3千多發子彈及多件槍械組件。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子已被暫控一項無牌管有槍械或彈藥罪，現正被扣留調查，案件將於明日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。被捕女子則已獲保釋候查，須於3月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，無牌管有槍械或彈藥為非常嚴重的刑事罪行，一經定罪，最高可處罰款港幣10萬及監禁14年，市民切勿以身試法。"},{"pid":"bb877fbc0b4d2a89f87762ba374237b319bdb8ff","tid":1035720,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T19:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4178c3a9e7c8ab4e6bb761febafa7c684ae0bc","tid":1035720,"uid":15743,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T19:10:02.000Z","msg":"長嗰啲好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8490c222121bdc5d8ac67d12f0e9434